snippet: Top seed Serena Williams turned an early challenge into an eventual cakewalk as she beat Russian-born Yulia Putintseva 7-6(2) 6-0 in the third round of the BNP Paribas Open in California on Sunday....
lead_paragraph: Top seed Serena Williams turned an early challenge into an eventual cakewalk as she beat Russian-born Yulia Putintseva 7-6(2) 6-0 in the third round of the BNP Paribas Open in California on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Serena Williams Wins Third-Round Match at Indian Wells
headline.main: Serena Williams Wins Third-Round Match at Indian Wells
